	How to create an web application in eclipse?
	
	File  -> new -> others -> web -> dynamic web project

	
	All HTMl Files in the WebContent.
	
	1. Web.xml 
			<welcome-file> - tells the first document execute.
					         It checks files one by one. If no files exists then it will give error.
	
	2. By default HTTP port is 8080.
	3. Create index.html page in the webContent
	